<paragraph id="2544368A2511FF90FF45155EFBA1FBD5" blockId="4.[178,1085,1036,1146]" pageId="4" pageNumber="1619">
Comment: The original description is based on a male 
<typeStatus id="FA4088282511FF90FCDA155EFC14FB8D" box="[813,902,1036,1058]" pageId="4" pageNumber="1619">holotype</typeStatus>
and 
<specimenCount id="33FDFD032511FF90FC4C155EFBAFFB8D" box="[955,1085,1036,1058]" pageId="4" pageNumber="1619" type="generic" typeStatus="paratypes">15 paratypes</specimenCount>
from &quot;Mt. Maya-san, 
<collectingRegion id="E73FF8682511FF90FE661578FD83FBEF" box="[401,529,1066,1088]" country="Japan" name="Hyogo" pageId="4" pageNumber="1619">Hyôgo Pref.</collectingRegion>
&quot; (
<bibRefCitation id="416A4B7B2511FF90FDD11578FD4FFBEF" author="WATANABE Y" box="[550,733,1066,1088]" pageId="4" pageNumber="1619" pagination="183 - 190" refId="ref11783" refString="WATANABE Y. (2008): Two new species of Lathrobium (Coleoptera: Staphylinidae) from Mt. Maya-san of Hyogo Prefecture in Western Honshu, Japan. - Taichius, Special Publication of the Japan Coleopterological Society, Osaka 2: 183 - 190." type="journal article" year="2008">WATANABE 2008</bibRefCitation>
). Based on the synapomorphically derived morphology of the aedeagus and the shape and chaetotaxy of the male sternites VII and VIII, 
<taxonomicName id="E2FB4D092511FF90FEC81537FE09FBD5" authorityName="WATANABE" authorityYear="2008" box="[319,411,1124,1146]" class="Insecta" family="Staphylinidae" genus="Lathrobium" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="4" pageNumber="1619" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="taichii">
<emphasis id="178FEA982511FF90FEC81537FE09FBD5" box="[319,411,1124,1146]" italics="true" pageId="4" pageNumber="1619">L. taichii</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
is closely related to 
<taxonomicName id="E2FB4D092511FF90FD9C1537FD67FBD5" authorityName="WATANABE" authorityYear="1991" box="[619,757,1124,1146]" class="Insecta" family="Staphylinidae" genus="Lathrobium" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="4" pageNumber="1619" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="sanukiense">
<emphasis id="178FEA982511FF90FD9C1537FD67FBD5" box="[619,757,1124,1146]" italics="true" pageId="4" pageNumber="1619">L. sanukiense</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
, 
<taxonomicName id="E2FB4D092511FF90FCF51537FCFFFBD5" authorityName="WATANABE" authorityYear="1992" box="[770,877,1124,1146]" class="Insecta" family="Staphylinidae" genus="Lathrobium" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="4" pageNumber="1619" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="shingon">
<emphasis id="178FEA982511FF90FCF51537FCFFFBD5" box="[770,877,1124,1146]" italics="true" pageId="4" pageNumber="1619">L. shingon</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
, and allied species.
</paragraph>
